    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Mehen ",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "is thought to be a board game played by ancient Egyptians during the First to Sixth Dynasties. Various types of "
        },
        {
          "text": "Mehen ",
          "italic": true
        },
        {
          "text": "boards have been found throughout different tombs, suggesting that it was a popular game."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "\n"
        }
      ]
    },
